skins.title: Mod Pack 1
skins.description: In Garry's Mod, players have the ability to create and manipulate objects in a virtual environment, and one of the most powerful and destructive tools available to them is the bomb. A bomb is a type of explosive device that can be placed and detonated in the game, causing destruction and chaos in its wake. In this article, we will explore the different types of bombs available in Garry's Mod, their characteristics, and how they can be used to enhance the gameplay experience.

skins.title: Mod Pack 2
skins.description: Time Bomb: A time bomb is a type of explosive device that detonates after a set amount of time has elapsed. In Garry's Mod, players can set the timer for the bomb and then place it wherever they want. Once the timer runs out, the bomb will explode, causing damage and destruction to anything in its vicinity.

skins.title: Mod Pack 3
skins.description: Proximity Mine: A proximity mine is a type of explosive device that detonates when someone gets too close to it. In Garry's Mod, players can place proximity mines in strategic locations to defend their base or to surprise and kill unsuspecting enemies.

skins.title: Mod Pack 4
skins.description: Remote Bomb: A remote bomb is a type of explosive device that can be detonated by the player from a distance. In Garry's Mod, players can place remote bombs and then activate them using a remote detonator, which can be triggered from a safe distance.

skins.title: Mod Pack 5
skins.description: Sticky Bomb: A sticky bomb is a type of explosive device that can be attached to surfaces or objects. In Garry's Mod, players can attach sticky bombs to cars, walls, or other objects, and then detonate them at the right moment to cause maximum damage.

skins.title: Mod Pack 6
skins.description: Nuke: A nuke is a type of explosive device that is extremely powerful and destructive. In Garry's Mod, players can unleash a nuke to wipe out entire cities or bases, but the consequences of using a nuke can be severe.

skins.title: Mod Pack 7
skins.description: Blast Radius: The blast radius of a bomb is the area around the bomb that will be affected by the explosion. In Garry's Mod, players need to be careful when placing bombs, as the blast radius can cause damage to objects and structures in the game.
